Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且阳光好强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须涂些防晒效果更好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能稍微抵抗些阳光...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 太下流了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么大家能轻易地做如此不堪之事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血之网 柔软的RH+B
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:49.16,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(790,1000)}Blood Nate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:00:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是你救了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good job
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么你会突然从天上...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在练习跳入露天浴池的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞错方向跳到外面来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露天浴池？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 天音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是吸血鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从黑色世界 Darkness Embrace来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲的真祖 阿尔玛莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫天音 彩城天音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.96,0:01:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里蓝色世界的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么说你是人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是进化者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:47.60,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)}Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行的能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是α驱动者 所以不会飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你掉下来不就很糟糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实会死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是说"很危险呢"的时候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险的是你自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是"啊哈哈"的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天音 我来做你的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个宇宙中共有五个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色世界 Darknesse Embrace
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色世界 Terra Rubri Aurora
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白色世界 System White Egma
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绿色世界 Gruneschild
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及 蓝色世界 这个地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然有一天 五个世界相连在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩坏的危机悄然而至
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了拯救将要灭亡的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在青兰岛上聚集了拥有特殊能力Exceed的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们称她们为进化者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.48,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1145,1000)}Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进化者通过与α驱动者加深羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:21.52,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(625,1000)}Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能发挥出强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了避免世界崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:30.37,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,1000)}World End
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们将与世界的敌人衔尾蛇战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:35.58,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1115,1000)}Uroboros
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会把你救出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是因为羁绊很弱才得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈亚...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击的进化者全都墮入黑暗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:25.70,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(805,1000)}Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,α驱动者的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过Link逆流到了进化者的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:30.33,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1105,1000)}Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说因为Link...羁绊很强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们的羁绊动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天音你怎么会理解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,α驱动者不可能会明白进化者的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:45.47,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1175,1000)}Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托这个福我们得救了 真是讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天音醒过来了我须要向她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间让你们想这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天音也是有错的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔玛莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看天音那样 其实气量很小
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常冒失 也很喜欢撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有我陪着就什么事都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是个不行的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有到这个地步...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 羁绊太弱不只是纱夜你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有我太惯着天音的错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会拯救天音的 因为我是她的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是舒爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发自内心的放松原来这么舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赐予我们墮入黑暗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忠于自己内心生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正的光明世界的居民吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能全部破坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能明确地和劲敌成为敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是无上的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 让我更快乐点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我内心渴求之物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此就稍微玩一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们绿色世界统合军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:31.91,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(930,1000)}Gruneschild
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更名为衔尾蛇特殊部队 是最精锐的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:35.29,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,1000)}Uroboros
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后也是能歼灭一切的无敌战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须随时磨练自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以愧对精英之名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有好好磨练自身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尤卡·佐奈木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过任务中不要叫姐姐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扬羽·佐奈木中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 接下来要对你进行特别训练
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别训练？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是长官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算对方是可爱的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也必须派你去进行危险的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是在多么严酷的战场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也抱着希望你能平安归来的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许叫我姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 中佐阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 今天就进行关于野外求生获取食物的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野外求生获取食物？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战场上有时会需要自己去获取食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是去捕获猎物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有必须注意的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 毒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大自然中有着许多有毒的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要避开它们进食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要如何区分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是要进行这方面的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的俄罗斯饭团转盘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能吃的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余的都放了超辣酱料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会只让你进行如此危险的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会一起吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别阻止我 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能让重要的妹妹一个人在危险中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尤卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你叫我中佐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好觉悟了吗 马尤卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 纱夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向前辈你没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了很多过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱夜你不够努力之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有想着去理解天音什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你们两人的羁绊才会很弱之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 纱夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 都是因为墮入黑暗的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向前辈也不是说的真心话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真心话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向前辈的话句句都说到心坎里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有试着去理解天音 完全是在白忙活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就和天音拉远了心灵的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要战胜弱小的自己 变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为EXR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和天音一起作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会拯救天音的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米哈伊尔博士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体的情况还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性能量Extra的减少速度正在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是和众多的进化者墮入黑暗有关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:18.47,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)}Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也只能这么想了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Extra消耗完的话 五个世界就会相撞毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 之前的战斗中Extra有暂时性的恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 观测到各个世界的接近速度有所下降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是因为解救了日向美海 所以她所拥有的Extra解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 只要把墮入黑暗的进化者击败的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:47.79,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,1000)}Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许就能拯救世界了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库拉拉你又说的这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明只是个C等级
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米哈伊尔博士 您看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 尤菲莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色世界的Extra正在急剧减少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接近速度又重新升高了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是世界水晶...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界水晶是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界水晶是在各个世界的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Extra的结晶体 支撑世界之物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙的目的是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果世界水晶消失的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Extra就会完全消失 世界就会...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有必要前往黑色世界进行调查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是青兰岛的防御也不能松懈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除去我们 现存的进化者只有C和UC等级
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:54.03,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(975,1000)}Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现状来考虑 让她们去会比较危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须要保护这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护下来 拯救天音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色世界是我出生的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:14.34,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,1000)}Darkness Embrace
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上红莲真祖之名 我会保护好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很麻烦 我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿乌罗拉 她们全都还只是UC
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在龙神诸岛救出美海的就是她们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家前往黑色世界进行调查
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青兰岛由我们来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿乌罗拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 阿乌罗拉也是EXR
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我也是C等级
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最底端的说什么大话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要救出你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是光环的内部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱夜你还是第一次去别的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色世界我也是第一次去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也只了解白色世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以拜托你了 阿尔玛莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色世界是我和敬爱的索菲娜前辈的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:46.35,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(525,1000)}Darkness Embrace
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常熟悉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔玛莉亚你和索菲娜前辈关系很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 索菲娜前辈很会照顾人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是位很好的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因为自尊心很高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦要给她撑面子就会不高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人也是没有我就不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊 阿尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量完全不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 索菲娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 不振作点就没法成为我一样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我会努力成为像索菲娜前辈那样最高级EXR的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 阿尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有好好吸过血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸血什么的 太难为情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是吸血鬼 要好好吸血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算您这么说 我觉得不需要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你装什么乖孩子 其实明明很想吸的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要吸我的试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么吸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲娜前辈 请您要平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是黑色世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 是我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷电？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yell-friend
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:02.69,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)}Blood Lance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露艾露 不要在我之前先使用我的招数啊
