Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是 黑色世界伟大的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 阿尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲娜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你会来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墮入黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 我来当你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就和它玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色世界伟大的意志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔玛莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点这些家伙很强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑枢城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是瞄准世界水晶的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,障壁 必须要阻止它才行
