Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我好好疼爱你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血之盾
