Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心 这些家伙是进化者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:11.28,Pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1180,1000)}Progress
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 阿尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认真起来就这点程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输血跟不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 因为你是阿尔玛啊
